data.description: First time home buyers. Don't miss out on this 3 bedroom, 2 bath home with tile floors throughout the main living areas, with updated bathrooms and kitchen with newer appliances! Fenced in backyard and plenty of storage room via a one car garage, separate indoor storage room off of garage and 2 large sheds. Also a covered carport to park your car or boat and protect it from the hot Florida sun! New roof in 2016 and new electrical panel in 2022. Newer hot water heater and garage door opener. Home has high efficiency window units for AC & heat that keep the home plenty cool. Screened in porch overlooking the backyard. This home is high and dry and not currently located in a flood zone, however, it is in close proximity to Inverness's famous chain of lakes.
